    "content" : "<blockquote>\n <div>\n  <cite>wizard 1066 wrote:</cite>It's been in for a couple of years now and we have just renewed all the bushes and greased everything, to find it now stiff to use, it might be down to the spacer compressing or just the parts need wearing in, going to try to fit a couple of washers under the spacer to see if it makes any difference.\n </div>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<br>It'll be the spring ring that goes around the plastic bushing under the gear shift plate under the front floor. I had exactly the same issue with mine that i recently replaced.",
