    "content" : "<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_bounce.gif\" alt=\":bounce:\" title=\"bounce\"> Evening all \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_bounce.gif\" alt=\":bounce:\" title=\"bounce\"> \n<br>\n<br>Just a quickie as wiring and soldering isn't very photogenic. I redid bits of wiring for the warning lights to the fuel pump/solenoid and warning lights\n<br>\n<br>I've been mulling something over in my head for a few days and tonight I fabbed this up.\n<br>\n<br>So folks…….it's\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 200%; line-height: 116%;\"><span style=\"color: #FF8000\">****COMPETITION TIME ****</span></span>\n<br>\n<br>A free beer at VF to the first person that guesses what it is. All will be revealed later in the week \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\"> \n<br>\n<br>Mystery item displayed in vice\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s790.photobucket.com/user/stevejones3163/media/Rusty2/IMAG3049_zpsfqdb0z09.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i790.photobucket.com/albums/yy185/stevejones3163/Rusty2/IMAG3049_zpsfqdb0z09.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<br>Mystery item painted\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://s790.photobucket.com/user/stevejones3163/media/Rusty2/IMAG3050_zpspalff52o.jpg.html\" class=\"postlink\"><img src=\"http://i790.photobucket.com/albums/yy185/stevejones3163/Rusty2/IMAG3050_zpspalff52o.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\n<br>\n<br>I also had a little play with the Vespa. It still runs and very well too. I'm amazed at how well it runs, considering what its been through. But it cuts out when I turn the headlights on. I'll have to collect the chips in the daylight \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<br>\n<br>Cheers\n<br>\n<br>Steve",
